Author: tseokii
Text: Yes! Stretching is so good.  Also, for any students, I really recommend stretch breaks while studying. It doesn't even have to be anything fancy either. I usually just stand up, sick my arms way out, stretch them up, reach for my toes, and then reverse. It's just a little thing but I find it beneficial, makes me feel like a human again after I've been drowning in my work haha
